{
  "stem": "16059.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was becoming apparent that they couldn't live there anymore.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So Erna, my mother, made contact with this gentleman.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my mother thought that Brussels might be better, a better life.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And possibly we could be free there for the future.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She went to see this gentleman and asked him would he take us across the border somehow.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he said, no, he refused her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He said he couldn't do it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the constraints were we did have a grandma, which is, which, who was my father's mother, paternal grandmother.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she was older, and there were a lot of things to be concerned about because it meant going on foot across the border.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so this gentleman at first, like I said, refused.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my mother pleaded and begged with him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he finally gave in to do this for us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So my parents made preparations to do this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we paid him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was paid.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Money, German money.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know the amount, I don't know an amount.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But this is something he did for a living.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was a good Samaritan, he did this with his heart.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But of course, you know, he did get paid.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I cannot recall his name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I don't think my parents can, either.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's been so long ago.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We-- [SIGH] we prepared to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We took nothing with us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "As I said, I was just a year old.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was grandma, who was just a little sickly, slow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He explained to us, came to us, explained to us how he was going to do this, that we could have nothing on our persons, that I had to be kept quiet, that silence and speed was of the utmost importance.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we would have to go through the forest.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
